Marysville.Getchell, Washington:
Getchell is an unincorporated community in Snohomish County, in the U.S. state of Washington.


== History ==
Getchell was laid out in the 1890s by L. W. Getchell, and named for him. A post office called Getchell was established in 1890, and remained in operation until 1918.
